These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, zinnia
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, coach, teacher
1. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Flower     | iris | aconite    | zinnia   |
| Job   | librarian  | teacher | coach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-2::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, bird
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, roller, trike
1. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |       3       |
| Pet      | rat   | bird  | turtle |
| Transport   | roller | bus | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, april, may
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, ice-hockey, basketball
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
3. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | april | may | august |
| Sport           | ice-hockey    | basketball     | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, oliveros, dunhill
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, skateboard, van
1. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
2. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
4. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Cigar    | dunhill | vegafina     | oliveros   |
| Transport   | skateboard   | subway | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, december, november
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, volleyball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Birthday   | december | october | november   |
| Sport     | volleyball | swimming    | badminton |

