.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-6::.
City: edinburgh, london, hamburg
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy, drama
1. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
3. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| City         | london | edinburgh | hamburg |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific   | comedy   | drama        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-7::.
City: london, marseilles, miami
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, boat
1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
2. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
3. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |     2      |         3          |
| City     | london | miami    | marseilles |
| Transport   | quad-bike      | boat | jet-ski             |

