.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, spanish
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, whist
1. the dutch is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the dutch is on the right of the spanish##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the spanish##3
4. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | spanish | dutch  | brazilian    |
| Game     | whist   | monopoly | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-9::.
House: art-deco, modern, colonial
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, red, orange
1. the colonial house is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the modern house##1
4. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |    3     |
| House    | art-deco       | modern   | colonial |
| Color   | red | azure | orange  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, camping
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, tram, bike
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the tram##2
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby           | hiking | traveling | camping |
| Transport   | tram   | helicopter      | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-11::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, surfing, swimming
There 3 different types of food: tomato, corn, blueberry
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Sport      | swimming   | lacrosse     | surfing      |
| Food   | blueberry | corn | tomato |

