.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, tennis, skateboarding
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, january
1. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
3. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |    3    |
| Sport        | rowing | tennis | skateboarding |
| Birthday   | october  | june         | january   |

