.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-13::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, havana, alhambra
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, aquamarine, blue
1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
3. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blue##5
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | alhambra          | havana     | swisher  |
| Color         | blue | yellow | aquamarine |

