.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, reading, filmmaking
3 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, snooker
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Hobby   | traveling | reading       | filmmaking |
| Game         | go | snooker | mah-jongg |

