.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, garlic
1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5
4. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage           | fanta | cola | soy-milk |
| Food   | garlic   | lettuce      | grapefruit  |

