.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, project-manager, security-guard
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, alhambra, davidoff
1. the architect is in the middle##1
2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |  3   |
| Job   | project-manager | architect | security-guard  |
| Cigar     | chaman | davidoff   | alhambra |

 